lot of people don't

00:01:28.150 --> 00:01:29.800 align:middle line:84%
know a lot of
literature, culture,

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:32.090 align:middle line:90%
art was created in dream states.

00:01:32.090 --> 00:01:34.900 align:middle line:84%
