00:02:06.805 --> 00:02:08.680 align:middle line:84%
How you do anything is
how you do everything.

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:10.300 align:middle line:90%
And success breeds success.

00:02:10.300 --> 00:02:11.520 align:middle line:90%
And why not start with a win?

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:14.330 align:middle line:84%
That only takes you one or two
minutes to be able to do that.

00:02:14.330 --> 00:02:17.290 align:middle line:84%
