00:02:20.650 --> 00:02:22.570 align:middle line:84%
You come back to
your bed, right.

00:02:22.570 --> 00:02:23.802 align:middle line:90%
So you go full circle.

00:02:23.802 --> 00:02:26.260 align:middle line:84%
Another thing I do every single
morning in terms of habits,

00:02:26.260 --> 00:02:30.250 align:middle line:84%
