brain muscles.

00:02:56.530 --> 00:02:59.260 align:middle line:84%
Because as your body
moves, your brain grooves.

00:02:59.260 --> 00:03:00.910 align:middle line:84%
They did a study at
Oxford University

00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:02.190 align:middle line:90%
