00:03:02.190 --> 00:03:04.360 align:middle line:84%
They found that jugglers
actually had bigger brains.

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:06.742 align:middle line:84%
They created more white
matter in their brains

00:03:06.742 --> 00:03:08.950 align:middle line:84%
because as you move your
body, it actually stimulates

00:03:08.950 --> 00:03:10.030 align:middle line:90%
different parts of your brain.

00:03:10.030 --> 00:03:12.030 align:middle line:84%
Because it's not just the
brain/body connection,

00:03:12.030 --> 00:03:13.510 align:middle line:90%
it's a body/brain connection.

00:03:13.510 --> 00:03:15.130 align:middle line:84%
And that's what
science is telling us.

