your child, that really shows

00:04:21.620 --> 00:04:22.420 align:middle line:90%
up.

00:04:22.420 --> 00:04:25.207 align:middle line:84%
So you do it for physiological
reasons, for inflammation.

00:04:25.207 --> 00:04:27.040 align:middle line:84%
But you also do it for
psychological reasons

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.498 align:middle line:84%
because you're
building resilience.

00:04:28.498 --> 00:04:30.380 align:middle line:84%
You're building
grit also, as well.

